(11956, 1314, 'bottom_text', 'Bakery accessories are your best friends in the kitchen. They will help you do small yet significant things like separating egg whites, cool the cake, or cut the cookies. WhisQ has a range of exciting baking accessories which add fun to your baking experience. One can make muffins effortlessly in the muffin cups or use heart shaped silicone cupcake moulds to prepare cute cupcakes. The bakeware also has an exclusive range of egg separators, muffin cups, cake moulds, chocolate moulds, loaf and bundt pans, cooling racks, silicone mats, measuring cups and spoons etc.\r\n\r\nWhisQ offers a variety in terms of cookie cutters, chocolate melting pots, cake stencils, cake and cupcake stand and cake decorating tools. All the products are made using German technology and promise premium quality. Buy this pocket-friendly bakeware online with WhisQ.'),
