(3299, 594, 'top_content', '<h3></h3>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\nFuture Group’s <strong>WhisQ </strong>is a brand that caters to every home baker''s needs by providing a full range of baking equipment. Made with the best German technology, these equipments are a class apart.\r\n\r\nWhisQ takes you from the basics of baking to the finesse of the final dish. From fondant rollers, whisks, cake decorating kit, macaroon kit, to moulds, tins and measuring spoons, these products are made keeping in mind all the factors which will take your baking experience a step higher.\r\n\r\nAt WhisQ, you will find a range of beautiful baking pans in varied shapes to make tiered cakes, muffins, dainty fairy cakes, and tarts. Baking pretty macarons is a breeze with our silicone baking mats and seasoned cake decorators can create breathtaking fondant art using our range of precision tools.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
