(10911, 1288, 'bottom_text', 'Mixing bowls are one of the basic tools required to prepare delicious dessert recipes. The better the quality of the bowl, the easier is the baking process. WhisQ has introduced a range of small and large mixing bowls which are microwave safe. One can melt chocolate or just combine the flour and the cream to bake cakes in this bakery equipment.\r\n\r\nThe bowls are made using German technology and offer supreme quality. Moreover, these products are fairly priced, making them must-have baking accessories. WhisQ has made sure that there will never be a dull moment while you prepare your cakes, muffins etc as these mixing bowls come in various colors.'),
(10912, 1288, '_bottom_text', 'field_5979b4d7f3c2c'),
(10913, 1288, 'bottom_banner', '1000'),
(10914, 1288, '_bottom_banner', 'field_5979b513f3c2d'),
