(10917, 1289, 'bottom_text', 'A pan is one of the base accessories required to prepare any baking recipe. To enhance your baking experience, WhisQ has introduced a series of pans which suit your different needs. Each cake and bakery product needs a particular kind of pan with specific dimensions. The pan required to bake a cake will differ from the one required to bake muffins and loafs.\r\n\r\nWhisQ understands this necessity and has introduced a series of exclusive bakeware. Each pan has a different shape, dimension, and diameter which fulfills your need of having a customized pan for each recipe. The products are made by using German technology and promise a high quality. Buy cake pan, baking pan, bundt pan, muffin pan and loaf pan online with WhisQ.'),
