(11398, 1300, 'bottom_text', 'Each tart you make, each cake you bake and each cupcake you decorate needs a lot of attention and patience. The long hours in the kitchen are enjoyable but can be tiring if you do not use the right kind of equipment. We absolutely believe that ''where there is WhisQ there is a way''. To make your baking process easier WhisQ has introduced an assortment of bakery equipment and accessories like pans, whisks, spatulas, piping bags and cookie cutters.\r\n\r\nFuture Group''s WhisQ brings all kinds of baking utensils and gizmos under one roof. A paradise for home bakers, the equipment uses German technology and are priced starting Rs.500, assuring pocket-friendly products. Bake with the finest equipment and feel the difference in your end products. Experiment with different kinds of fondants, macarons, cakes, tarts, pies, and muffins in varied shapes and styles with WhisQ''s range of bakeware.'),
