(11410, 1302, 'bottom_text', 'Whisks and spatulas are essential accessories to bake any recipe. Without this bakeware, your process of making cakes seems incomplete. You need whisks to blend the ingredients, smoothen the batter etc. Spatulas are multi-functional which are used for spreading the cream, lifting and flipping cakes etc. Hence, each baking recipe demands a particular kind of whisk and spatula.\r\n\r\nWhisQ has a range of bakery equipment which is fairly priced and offers high quality. Made from German technology, whisks and spatulas have multiple sizes and variants wherever applicable. Browse through the range of egg beaters, egg whisks, balloon whisks, silicone spatulas, offset spatulas, icing spatulas, cake spatulas and pastry brushes and buy similar bakeware online.'),
(11411, 1302, '_bottom_text', 'field_5979b4d7f3c2c'),
(11412, 1302, 'bottom_banner', '1000'),
(11413, 1302, '_bottom_banner', 'field_5979b513f3c2d'),
