(11415, 55, '_edit_lock', '1507887565:1'),
(11416, 1303, 'top_content', '<h3></h3>\r\n<h4></h4>\r\nFuture Group’s <strong>WhisQ </strong>is a brand that caters to every home baker''s needs by providing a full range of baking equipment. Made with the best German technology, these equipments are a class apart.\r\n\r\nWhisQ takes you from the basics of baking to the finesse of the final dish. From fondant rollers, whisks, cake decorating kit, macaroon kit, to moulds, tins and measuring spoons, these products are made keeping in mind all the factors which will take your baking experience a step higher.\r\n\r\nAt WhisQ, you will find a range of beautiful baking pans in varied shapes to make tiered cakes, muffins, dainty fairy cakes, and tarts. Baking pretty macarons is a breeze with our silicone baking mats and seasoned cake decorators can create breathtaking fondant art using our range of precision tools.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;'),
(11417, 1303, '_top_content', 'field_59a96023cfd5e'),
(11418, 1303, 'top_side_image', '683'),
(11419, 1303, '_top_side_image', 'field_59a96033cfd5f'),
(11420, 1303, 'what_title', '<h3><strong>PRODUCTS MADE WITH LOVE</strong></h3>\r\nEvery product under our label is made with utmost care to cater to every home baker’s needs. You have to try it to believe it!'),
(11421, 1303, '_what_title', 'field_59a9604ccfd60'),
(11422, 1303, 'second_image', '685'),
(11423, 1303, '_second_image', 'field_59a96062cfd61'),
(11424, 1303, 'second_content', 'From Mumbai to Delhi and everywhere in between, the classic, chic, and essential baking tools that WhisQ brings to you make baking a completely enjoyable time. No longer do you have to worry about messy baking at home where the time taken to bake is the most arduous time of your life. Make it easy with our collection of tools to make desserts at home.'),
(11425, 1303, '_second_content', 'field_59a9607acfd62'),
(11426, 1303, 'third_image', '686'),
(11427, 1303, '_third_image', 'field_59a9608ccfd63'),
(11428, 1303, 'third_content', 'Every product is tried &amp; tested. Whether you want to bake that perfect cheesecake or a dozen perfectly risen and frosted cupcakes, WhisQ helps you make your wildest creations into a reality. There’s no limit to what you can make with our products.'),
(11429, 1303, '_third_content', 'field_59a960a5cfd64'),
(11430, 1303, 'fourth_image', '687'),
(11431, 1303, '_fourth_image', 'field_59a960cdcfd65'),
(11432, 1303, 'fourth_content', 'Our vast collection of pans, measuring cups &amp; spoons, fondant decorating tools and so on are perfect to help you create the most delicious and innovative desserts. So go on and shop to make your baking dreams a reality.'),
(11433, 1303, '_fourth_content', 'field_59a960ebcfd66'),
(11434, 1303, 'bottom_content', 'Our entire collection is available at select stores in India.'),
