(793, 1, '2017-09-12 11:41:56', '2017-09-12 11:41:56', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Non-stick finish inside the pan allows baked goods to release easily from the pan while making clean up simple.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavyweight steel construction ensures even heating for optimal baking results.</li>\r\n 	<li>Scratch resistant.</li>\r\n 	<li>Dishwasher safe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use only nylon or wooden utensils along with this pan.</li>\r\n</ul>', '9 inch Round Cake Pan', 'Ideal for baked goods, this round cake pan is crafted with a heavyweight steel core that distributes heat quickly for even baking. Scratch resistant and dishwasher safe, it’s non-stick finish prevents overcooking &amp; promotes easy release and quick clean up.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '9-round-cake-pan', '', '', '2017-10-13 10:25:24', '2017-10-13 10:25:24', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=793', 0, 'product', '', 0),
