(795, 1, '2017-09-12 12:02:34', '2017-09-12 12:02:34', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Makes 6 cupcakes or muffins in one go. Bake delicious cupcakes, fairy cakes and buns.</li>\r\n 	<li>Food grade non-stick coating.</li>\r\n 	<li>Heavy-gauge construction provides even-heating performance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Easy to clean and safe to use in a dishwasher.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use only nylon or wooden utensils along with this pan.</li>\r\n</ul>', '6 Cup Muffin Pan', 'This German-made non-stick muffin pan is designed to bake six delicious cupcakes, fairy cakes, buns or muffins in a jiffy. The pan’s non-stick coating prevents sticking and cleans up in seconds.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '6-cup-muffin-pan', '', '', '2017-10-13 10:25:14', '2017-10-13 10:25:14', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=795', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(787, 1, '2017-09-12 10:19:45', '2017-09-12 10:19:45', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ideal for cakes.</li>\r\n 	<li>Even heat distribution.</li>\r\n 	<li>Carbon steel pan provides quick and even cooking and ensures optimal browning. The non-stick coating prevents overcooking.</li>\r\n 	<li>Can be used in OTG, microwave (in convection mode) and pressure cookers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Effortless quick cleaning and dishwasher safe.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use only nylon or wooden utensils along with this pan.</li>\r\n</ul>', '8 inch Square Cake Pan', 'Ideal for brownies, cookie crusts and more, this square pan is crafted with a carbon steel core that distributes heat and cools quickly for even baking. It also ensures optimal browning and its non-stick layers prevent overcooking &amp; promote easy release and quick clean up. The rolled edges boost the pan''s durability for years of use.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '8-square-cake-pan', '', '', '2017-10-14 09:02:16', '2017-10-14 09:02:16', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=787', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(789, 1, '2017-09-12 11:10:34', '2017-09-12 11:10:34', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Perfect for baking three-layered cakes, cheesecakes, coffee cakes, pizzas, frozen desserts and more.</li>\r\n 	<li>The removable bottom can be detached and is held firmly using a spring bracket.</li>\r\n 	<li>Carbon steel construction and reinforced non-stick coating offer quick release and easy cleanup.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use in ovens &amp; freezers. Dishwasher safe and heat resistant up to 230 degree Celsius.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use only nylon or wooden utensils along with this pan.</li>\r\n</ul>', '11 inch Rectangular Cake Pan', 'Ideal for baked goodies, this rectangular pan is crafted with a carbon steel core that distributes heat and cools quickly for even baking. Its solid design ensures optimal browning and its non-stick layers prevent overcooking &amp; promote easy release and quick clean up.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '11-rectangular-cake-pan', '', '', '2017-10-13 10:25:33', '2017-10-13 10:25:33', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=789', 0, 'product', '', 0),
