(866, 1, '2017-09-13 13:45:01', '2017-09-13 13:45:01', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bake cookies, buns, pizzas or roast a chicken without letting them stick to the tray.</li>\r\n 	<li>Virgin food grade durable and resistant material that can withstand temperatures between -40 TO +240O C.</li>\r\n 	<li>It won''t absorb tastes or smells.</li>\r\n 	<li>Smooth on both sides.</li>\r\n 	<li>No need to grease as it is absolutely non-stick.</li>\r\n 	<li>Can be used in microwave, OTG or freezer.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use for rolling fondant/sugar paste or pastry sheets.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Silicone Baking Mat', 'Before baking your next batch of cookies, pizza, sticky buns or roasting a chicken, cover the pan/tray with this flexible baking sheet and enjoy the difference it makes. Reusable due to the durable &amp; resistant material, the silicone-coated sheet doesn’t absorb tastes or smells and is smooth on both sides. It needs no greasing as it’s a total non–stick.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'silicone-baking-mat', '', '', '2017-10-13 10:14:39', '2017-10-13 10:14:39', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=866', 0, 'product', '', 0),
