(868, 1, '2017-09-13 13:51:05', '2017-09-13 13:51:05', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Ideal for both beginners and experienced decorators.</li>\r\n 	<li>This simple, easy-to-use set allows you to precisely and professionally add magic to that party.</li>\r\n 	<li>Multiple nozzles allow various thickness &amp; patterns.</li>\r\n 	<li>Virgin food grade material.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Disposable Piping Bag Set', 'Ready for filling with fresh buttercream, royal icing and other frostings, these clear piping bags make it quick and easy to pipe decorations onto cakes, cupcakes and cookies. Ideal for both beginners and experienced decorators, the piping bag contains multiple nozzles that allow various thickness and patterns. Durable and disposable, they also eliminate mess.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'disposable-piping-bag-set', '', '', '2017-10-13 10:14:29', '2017-10-13 10:14:29', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=868', 0, 'product', '', 0),
