(996, 1, '2017-09-18 13:06:31', '2017-09-18 13:06:31', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Perfect for baking three-layered cakes, cheesecakes, coffee cakes, pizzas, frozen desserts and much more.</li>\r\n 	<li>The removable bottom can be detached and is held firmly using a spring bracket.</li>\r\n 	<li>Carbon steel construction and reinforced non-stick coating offer a quick release and easy cleanup.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use in ovens &amp; freezers. Dishwasher safe and heat resistant up to 230 degree Celsius.</li>\r\n 	<li>Use only nylon or wooden utensils along with this pan.</li>\r\n</ul>', '7 inch Round Spring Form Pan', 'Generations of great bakers have relied on classic springform pans like this one to create everything from perfect cheesecakes, three-layered cakes, coffee cakes, frozen desserts to savoury deep-dish pizzas and much more. Made from carbon steel for even baking, the pan is finished with a reinforced nonstick coating that guarantees effortless release with quick cleanup. The pan is dishwasher safe &amp; heat resistant and its removable bottom can be detached and is held firmly using a spring bracket.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '7-round-spring-form-pan', '', '', '2017-10-14 08:53:18', '2017-10-14 08:53:18', '', 0, 'http://www.togglehead.net/whisq/?post_type=product&#038;p=996', 0, 'product', '', 0),
