(40, 40, 'product_cat', 'Bakery accessories are your best friends in the kitchen. They will help you do small yet significant things like separating egg whites, cool the cake, or cut the cookies. WhisQ has a range of exciting baking accessories which adds fun to your baking experience. One can make muffins effortlessly in the muffin cups or use heart shaped silicone cupcake moulds to prepare cute cupcakes. The bakeware also has an exclusive range of egg separators, muffin cups, cake moulds, chocolate moulds, loaf and bundt pans, cooling racks, silicone mats, measuring cups and spoons etc.\r\n\r\nWhisQ offers a variety in terms of cookie cutters, chocolate melting pots, cake stencils, cake and cupcake stand and cake decorating tools. All the products are made using German technology and promise premium quality. Buy this pocket-friendly bakeware online with WhisQ.', 0, 29),
(41, 41, 'product_cat', 'Mixing bowls are one of the basic tools required to prepare delicious dessert recipes. The better the quality of the bowl, the easier is the baking process. WhisQ has introduced a range of small and large mixing bowls which are microwave safe. One can melt chocolate or just combine the flour and the cream to bake cakes in this bakery equipment. \r\n\r\nThe bowls are made using German technology and offer supreme quality. Moreover, these products are fairly priced, making them must-have baking accessories. WhisQ has made sure that there will never be a dull moment while you prepare your cakes, muffins etc as these mixing bowls come in various colors. ', 0, 2),
(42, 42, 'product_cat', 'Whisks and spatulas are essential accessories to bake any recipe. Without this bakeware, your process of making cakes seems incomplete. You need whisks to blend the ingredients, smoothen the batter etc. Spatulas are multi-functional which are used for spreading the cream, lifting and flipping cakes etc.  Hence, each baking recipe demands a particular kind of whisk and spatula.\r\n\r\nWhisQ has a range of bakery equipment which is fairly priced and offers high quality. Made from German technology, whisks and spatulas have multiple sizes and variants wherever applicable. Browse through the range of egg beaters, egg whisk, balloon whisk, silicone spatula, offset spatula, icing spatula, cake spatula and pastry brush and buy similar bakeware online.', 0, 8),
(68, 68, 'recipes_categories', '', 0, 5),
(69, 69, 'product_shipping_class', 'Shipping Change 100', 0, 47),
(70, 70, 'product_shipping_class', '_', 0, 2),
(43, 43, 'product_cat', 'A pan is one of the base accessories required to prepare any baking recipe. To enhance your baking experience, WhisQ has introduced a series of pans which suit your different needs. Each cake and bakery product need a peculiar kind of pan with specific dimensions. The pan required to bake a cake will differ from the one required to bake muffins and loafs.\r\n\r\nWhisQ understands this necessity and has introduced a series of exclusive bakeware. Each pan has a different shape, dimension and diameter which fulfills your need of having a customized pan for each recipe.  The products are made by using German technology and promise a high quality. Buy cake pan, baking pan, bundt pan, muffin pan and loaf pan online with WhisQ.', 0, 10),
